{"tid":601739,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam] Grim Dawn 特價(Titan Quest團隊續作)","createTime":"2018-03-22T12:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:57:00.000Z","uid":141043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3656467097fe37fb3535632e1fe1385e74ba010","tid":601739,"uid":141043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://humblebundle.imgix.net/misc/files/hashed/18eda5bccfb1095c66c64d0fdafef3983355ec5e.jpg?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=616&amp;h=353&amp;s=f054525da2f2c0ffcf56d1364ae48a01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumblebundle.imgix.net%2Fmisc%2Ffiles%2Fhashed%2F18eda5bccfb1095c66c64d0fdafef3983355ec5e.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D616%26h%3D353%26s%3Df054525da2f2c0ffcf56d1364ae48a01&h=a6fa98fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/219990/Grim_Dawn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F219990%2FGrim_Dawn%2F&d=fdLFOeRAS9c9pZiW6anb1qNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=23d460e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/219990/Grim_Dawn/</a><br />\n<br />\n(以下係以前啲巴打寫落)<br />\n特色： <br />\n1）雙職業系統,有好多種配搭 <br />\n<img src=\"http://grimdawn.com/webfiles/guide/gdx_classNames01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgrimdawn.com%2Fwebfiles%2Fguide%2Fgdx_classNames01a.jpg&h=72240344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）好似Poe，有個星座系統，但又有d唔同，呢個系統既技能點同職業系統分開計，要透過收集唔同地方既「聖壇」黎獲得星座用既技能點 <br />\n<br />\n3）唔同技能點法同裝備可以塑造唔同既流派玩法 <br />\n<br />\n4）RPG式劇情，劇情豐富，對話/決定影響結果，雖然ending不變（好似係） <br />\n（eg, 有個任叫你搵個工匠，搵到佢之後可以選擇殺左佢拎件裝/ 救佢黎番村幫你打造物品） <br />\n（有隻boss會扮成NPC呃你救佢番營地，係對話同場景中會有蛛絲馬跡睇到，但如果你選擇救佢，當你一番到村既時候就會發現佢係度殺緊營地d人） <br />\n<br />\n5）似WOW既聲望系統，唔同陣營既聲望會解鎖裝備/設計圖/更多精英怪出現 <br />\n<br />\n6）有槍械，有左輪有步槍 <br />\n<br />\n7) 睇評論d人話呢個團隊update隻game好密 <br />\n<br />\n8）steam而家只係賣緊 $37HKD <br />\n<br />\n9)官方有放文本出黎比人自己翻譯 <br />\n中文化（入面最底果個先係最新版）： <a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19441&amp;snA=32\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D19441%26snA%3D32&d=fdLFOeRAS9c9pZiW6anb1qNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=18b7727d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19441&amp;snA=32</a>"},{"pid":"67afee8fc62cde588bd58d5ea92352a7a657eb6f","tid":601739,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}